ZH: 我突然听到一声惊叫，吓了我一跳。
EN: I suddenly heard a scream, which startled me.

ZH: 他惊叫了一声，因为看到了一只蜘蛛。
EN: He let out a scream upon seeing a spider.

ZH: 姐姐看到了恐怖的场景，不禁惊叫出声。
EN: Upon witnessing a terrifying scene, my sister couldn't help but let out a scream.

ZH: 当突然有人大喊大叫时，我吓得惊叫一声。
EN: I screamed in shock when someone suddenly shouted loudly.

ZH: 那个小孩在海边惊叫着喊他爸爸。
EN: The child screamed and called out for his father at the beach.

ZH: 过山车速度越来越快，我不禁发出一声惊叫。
EN: As the roller coaster picked up speed, I couldn't help but let out a scream.

ZH: 她看到了一只大蛇，吓得惊叫了一声。
EN: She let out a scream upon seeing a large snake.

ZH: 当老鼠突然出现时，她惊叫了一声。
EN: She screamed in surprise when the mouse suddenly appeared.

ZH: 他听到了一个恶心的笑声，惊叫了一下。
EN: He screamed in shock upon hearing a creepy laughter.

ZH: 我们正在看一部恐怖电影时，她突然惊叫了一声。
EN: While we were watching a horror movie, she suddenly screamed.

ZH: 当他撞倒了一把刀，他惊叫了起来。
EN: He screamed when he accidentally knocked over a knife.

ZH: 那个女孩吓得惊叫了一声，因为遇到了一只大蟒蛇。
EN: The girl let out a scream in fear when she encountered a large python.

ZH: 当我打开门时，猫吓了一跳并惊叫了一声。
EN: The cat got startled and let out a scream when I opened the door.

ZH: 当那只狗突然冲过来时，我惊叫了一声。
EN: I screamed in surprise when the dog suddenly came running towards me.

ZH: 她走进屋子时，看到了一个阴影，吓得惊叫一声。
EN: Upon entering the room, she saw a shadow and let out a scream in fear.

ZH: 他被一个巨大的声音吓了一跳，随后惊叫起来。
EN: He got startled by a loud noise and then let out a scream.

ZH: 我被一只蜘蛛爬上腿时惊叫了一声。
EN: I screamed when a spider crawled up my leg.

ZH: 当风景气球开始升空时，人们惊叫欢呼。
EN: People screamed and cheered as the hot air balloon started to ascend.

ZH: 在过山车的高峰瞬间，乘客们发出了一片惊叫声。
EN: There was a chorus of screams from the passengers at the peak moment of the roller coaster.

ZH: 当魔术师突然消失时，观众们惊叫喝彩。
EN: The audience screamed and applauded when the magician suddenly disappeared.

ZH: 当他们看到飞机猛然起飞时，机场上的人们惊叫起来。
EN: People at the airport screamed when they saw the plane suddenly take off.
